data.description: Discover your new home in the peaceful Terracina Community! This charming single-level residence offers 3 beds, 2 baths, and a 2-car garage. Come inside to find a desirable great room perfect for entertaining. The recessed lighting and neutral palette create an inviting ambiance, complemented by tile flooring throughout. The impeccable kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite counters, ample white cabinetry, and a peninsula with a breakfast bar. The primary bedroom includes a full bathroom with a walk-in closet for your convenience. Out the back, you have a relaxing covered patio and enough room to create an additional seating area or space for BBQ. Conveniently located close to schools, shopping, and restaurants. Easy access to both I-17 & Loop 101! Don't miss this opportunity!
